column7:
Hi, 

I’m Vishal Srivastav, Head of Product for B2B at GoodLeap — a California-based unicorn fintech focused on sustainable home improvement financing.

GoodLeap has facilitated over $30 billion in loans for more than 1 million homeowners and partners with thousands of contractors nationwide. With over 5,000 active contractors and 200–300 new onboardings weekly, we’re now looking to completely replace our contractor onboarding process, which currently depends on Salesforce and manual reviews.

Our goal is to build a fully self-serve, AI-powered onboarding experience that eliminates Salesforce entirely and reduces onboarding time from 4–6 weeks to just 2–3 days.

Key areas we’re focused on include:
AI-based document review and risk decisioning
Automated execution of credit underwriting SOPs
